The '''Red Bull M.E.O. 2024: India''' is a [[Battlegrounds Mobile India|BGMI]] tournament under the '''''Red Bull M.E.O.''''' series. Organized by '''[https://www.redbull.com/in-en/hubs/gaming/ Red Bull Gaming]''' in association with '''Skyesports'''.

==About==
===Broadcast Talent===
{{box|start|padding=1em}}
