'''Revamp Master Series''' is a BGMI tournament.

==About==
===Format===
* '''Pre Quarter:''''' July 6th - 8th, 2026
** 64 teams, 3 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 16.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 12 team from each group (Total 48 teams)}} advance to Quarter Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Quarter Finals:''''' July 9th - 10th, 2026
** 48 teams, 2 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 3 groups of 16.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 team from each group (Total 24 teams)}} advance to Semi Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''''' July 12th - 13th, 2026
** 24 teams, 2 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 3 groups of 8.
** Round-robin format.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} advance to the Grand Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' July 14th - 17th, 2026
** 16 teams, 4 matchdays.
** 24 matches (6 each day).
** On Day 2, teams will earn {{Bgcolortext|up|2 points for every finish}} secured during the {{Bgcolortext|up|Stage 1 (first zone)}} of the match.

